data.description: This home is situated in the highly sought-after Western Branch neighborhood, making it a great choice for those looking for their first home. 1834 sq ft of living space and is positioned on a corner lot. The house is equipped with newer windows and window treatments, providing a more modern and energy-efficient atmosphere. The kitchen is adorned with custom oak cabinets & granite countertops. All appliances, including the washer and dryer, will be conveyed with the property and are also sold in their current condition. For outdoor enjoyment and family gatherings, there's a spacious, oversized deck. The property consists of two lots, allowing the new owner the potential for expansion. Look no further!
